<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <title>Bookeeboo</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="../stylesheets/main.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="../javascripts/thirdparty/jquery-ui/jquery-ui.min.css">
    <link href='http://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Roboto:400,700italic,900italic,900,700,500,500italic,300,100,400italic,100italic,300italic' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css'>

    <script src="../javascripts/thirdparty/jquery-1.11.1.min.js"></script>
    <script src="../javascripts/thirdparty/jquery-ui/external/jquery/jquery.js"></script>
    <script src="../javascripts/thirdparty/jquery-ui/jquery-ui.min.js"></script>
    <script src="../javascripts/main.js"></script>
    
  </head>
  <body>
  	<div class="wrapper">
  		<div class="container">
  			<header class="header-sm">
  				<h1 class="hd-reg">Bookeeboo</h1>
  				<a href="#" class="sign-out">Sign Out</a>
  			</header>

  			<section class="panel">
  				<div class="search">
  					<input type="text" placeholder="Search a book you want to add to our queue" class="input-field">
  				</div>

  				<div class="current-reading">
  					<div class="cover"></div>
  					<div class="details">
  					 <div class="mark">You are reading</div>
  					 <header class="cur-header">
  							<h3>Nice Book about kitten</h3>
  					 </header>
  					 <p>This book is written for cat-lovers. It's about cute and funny citten who escaped from his family. You'll see adventures of clever people who had sold their home to pay for detective who spent all money for one-way ticket to Australia.
             </p>
            <!-- slider -->
            <div class="pages">
              <div class="graded">
                <div class="first-page">1</div>
                <div class="slider">
                 <div class="page-display"></div>   
                </div>
              <div class="last-page"></div>
            </div>
              
            <div class="pages-settings">
              <ul class="minus">
                <li class="amount">1</li>
                <li class="amount">5</li>
                <li class="amount">10</li>
                <li class="operator">&#8211;</li>
              </ul>
              <ul class="plus">
                <li class="operator">+</li>
                <li class="amount">1</li>
                <li class="amount">5</li>
              <li class="amount">10</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
  </div>
  			</section>

  			<section class="unordered-books">
  				<div class="mark">Unordered</div>
  				<ul>

  				</ul>
  			</section>

  			<section class="ordered-books">
  				<ul>
  					<li></li>
  					<li></li>
  					<li></li>
  					<li></li>
  					<li></li>
  					<li></li>
  				</ul>
  			</section>
  		</div>
  	</div>
  </body>
</html>
